[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0084","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-20103","title":"ProFTPD 1.3.3c 版本源码后门隐藏命令任意命令执行漏洞","description":"ProFTPD 1.3.3c 官方源码包在 2010 年 11 月 28 日至 12 月 2 日期间被植入恶意后门，攻击者通过触发隐藏的 FTP 命令即可以 root 权限在服务器上执行任意 Shell 命令。该漏洞影响使用该版本源码编译安装的 ProFTPD 服务器，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 9.3，属严重级别供应链投毒型漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-2010-20103"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2025-08-20T16:15:34.137","updated":"2026-07-15T02:16:56.140","remediation":"立即从官方渠道重新下载并升级到 ProFTPD 1.3.3d 或更高版本（1.3.3d 已移除该后门），严禁使用 2010 年 11 月 28 日至 12 月 2 日期间下载的 1.3.3c 源码包或二进制文件。升级前校验官方 GPG 签名与 SHA 校验和，确认软件完整性；若已部署受影响版本，应重置服务器凭据并检查是否存在异常 root 权限命令执行记录作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.proftpd.org/","https://advisories.checkpoint.com/defense/advisories/public/2011/cpai-2010-151.html/","https://github.com/proftpd/proftpd","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework/master/modules/exploits/unix/ftp/proftpd_133c_backdoor.rb","https://web.archive.org/web/20111107212129/http://rsync.proftpd.org/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15662","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16921","https://www.vulncheck.com/advisories/proftpd-backdoor-command-execution","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/javascript/cves/2010/CVE-2010-20103.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-20103.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/javascript/cves/2010/CVE-2010-20103.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2c1abd567e9f51bcb187554798cc5956bd402e98/cves/2010/20xxx/CVE-2010-20103.json","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-20103.rules","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f75ab9c4d42c6ac0916ce14ac69865bf1dcbb973/2010/20xxx/CVE-2010-20103.json","https://github.com/runZeroInc/nuclei-templates/blob/8f3fd5c72f1f22f6a06e5a55b25636ecd659c5ba/javascript/cves/2010/CVE-2010-20103.yaml","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/ad98898aca7860353055ea2aee0af12336215af4/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6593a7cdb3db460855b778a366e9ba479f28af94/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-20103.json","https://github.com/ada-yq225/FIT2173/blob/5e8a299e2875d3c2f4f5368a8bb19983c19c8964/README.md","https://github.com/Tag59/agent_pentest/blob/676f3ee7b5f80943ba84bde9d23cbc2c65540f8e/tools.py"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0084.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0108","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4239","title":"Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 5.2 版本存在本地文件包含漏洞，攻击者可通过构造恶意文件路径参数，利用输入验证不当缺陷包含本地任意文件，进而读取敏感文件或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 5.2 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8（CRITICAL），攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意文件包含路径实现任意代码执行或敏感文件读取，危害等级严重。官方已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议用户尽快升级到修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4239"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2019-10-28T15:15:12.583","updated":"2026-06-16T23:24:25.063","remediation":"tags.<value>建议立即升级至 Tiki Wiki CMS Groupware 5.3 或更高版本（官方已在 5.3 修复该 LFI 漏洞）。若暂时无法升级，可在 Web 服务器层面限制对 tiki-print_multi_pages.php 等受影响脚本的访问，并配置 PHP 的 open_basedir 限制文件包含路径；同时在防火墙层面封禁可疑请求参数（如 page、lang 等）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/cve-2010-4239","https://dl.packetstormsecurity.net/1009-exploits/tikiwiki52-lfi.txt","https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2010-4239","https://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2010/11/22/9","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4239.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/04deea2d5c50b4720e70811dcb426620621d3261/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4239.json","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder1/cve-2010-4239-1997.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/bf9978ea592b7413bb96dfeb9db92cbd52bf0c3d/api/2010/CVE-2010-4239.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/cve-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Tiki%20Wiki%20CMS/CVE-2010-4239.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-4239_3.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2010-4239_2_1.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-4239-1997.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0116","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-5286","title":"Joomla! com_jstore 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Jstore（com_jstore）第三方扩展组件存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞，属于 CWE-22 类型缺陷。该组件在处理 index.php 页面的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与规范化，远程攻击者可构造包含 \"..\"（点点）序列的恶意 controller 参数提交请求，绕过目录访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码等敏感数据）。由于该组件作为 Joomla! 站点插件部署，凡安装并启用了存在漏洞版本 com_jstore 组件的 Joomla! 网站均受影响。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，CVSS 基础评分高达 10.0（满分），危害等级为严重，除文件读取外还可能存在其他未明确说明的安全影响。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-5286"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2012-11-26T23:55:01.300","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:28.973","remediation":"立即卸载或升级存在漏洞的 Jstore (com_jstore) 第三方组件至官方修复版本，并通过后台「扩展管理-管理」彻底移除该组件；若暂不能升级，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 的 .htaccess）中对 index.php 的 controller 参数做过滤，拒绝包含「../」「..%2f」等路径穿越字符的请求，同时配置 PHP 的 open_basedir 限制脚本可访问目录，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1010-exploits/joomlajstore-lfi.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/44053","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34837","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5286.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-5286.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5286.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e7bd0957d7eea7c21095268cca9721e428611ed/cves/2010/5xxx/CVE-2010-5286.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-5286-2032.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-5286-2031.yaml","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-5286-2034.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-5286_10.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/27/Artifact/Report.csv","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-5286-2034.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0116.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0115","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0115.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-5278","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9185,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10867}}","description":"MODx Revolution 2.0.2-pl 及更早版本的 manager/controllers/default/resource/tvs.php 文件存在路径遍历漏洞。当服务器 magic_quotes_gpc 配置被禁用时，程序未对 class_key 参数进行充分的过滤和校验，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在该参数中注入 \"..\"（点点）序列绕过目录限制，从而读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源代码等），造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞利用条件较为简单，攻击者只需构造包含目录遍历序列的恶意 HTTP 请求即可触发，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2010-5278"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2012-10-07T20:55:00.907","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:28.083","remediation":"建议立即升级 MODx Revolution 至 2.0.3 及以上版本，官方已在 2.0.3 版本修复该路径遍历漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可通过以下方式缓解：1) 在 php.ini 中开启 magic_quotes_gpc = On（PHP 5.4+ 已废弃）；2) 在 Web 服务器层面限制对 /manager/controllers/default/resource/tvs.php 的访问权限，仅允许受信 IP 访问后台管理目录；3) 部署 WAF 规则拦截包含 ../ 路径遍历载荷的 class_key 参数请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://modxcms.com/forums/index.php/topic%2C55104.0.html","http://modxcms.com/forums/index.php/topic%2C55105.msg317273.html","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1009-exploits/modx202pl-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/41638","http://www.johnleitch.net/Vulnerabilities/MODx.Revolution.2.0.2-pl.Local.File.Inclusion/49","http://www.osvdb.org/68265","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/43577","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/62073","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34788","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5278.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-5278.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5278.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-5278.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-5278-2028.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-5278-2030.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5278.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Apr/16/Reports/Report.csv","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/2010/CVE-2010-5278.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-5278_2.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-5278.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0115.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0114","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-5028","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9103,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10856}}","description":"Joomla! JExtensions JE Job (com_jejob) 组件 1.0 版本的 index.php 文件中 item 操作的 catid 参数存在 SQL 注入漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 catid 参数传递特制的 SQL 语句，执行任意 SQL 命令，导致数据库信息泄露、数据篡改甚至服务器完全沦陷。该漏洞影响使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，属高危漏洞。攻击者可构造恶意 catid 参数值（如 ' UNION SELECT ...）注入 SQL 语句，获取数据库敏感信息或写入 Webshell 进一步控制服务器。厂商已停止维护该组件，建议立即卸载或升级至安全版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-5028"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-11-02T21:55:16.997","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:00.103","remediation":"立即升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Harmistechnology JE Job (com_jejob) 1.0 组件，替换为官方已修复版本或停用该组件。临时缓解措施：在 Joomla 后台禁用 com_jejob 组件，并通过 Web 应用防火墙对 index.php 的 catid 参数做 SQL 注入过滤与输入校验，限制远程匿名访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39837","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12782","http://www.osvdb.org/64708","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40193","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1269","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58599","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12601","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5028.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-5028.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5028.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-5028.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-5028-2021.yaml","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2010/CVE-2010-5028.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-5028_24.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-5028.json","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2010/README.md","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-5028-2023.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Mar/19/Reports/lfiReport.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0113","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0113.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4977","title":"Miniwork Com Canteen 1.0 SQL注入漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Canteen（com_canteen）组件 1.0 版本在 menu.php 中存在 SQL 注入漏洞。该组件在处理用户请求时未对传入 index.php 的 mealid 参数进行严格的输入校验与转义，导致攻击者可通过构造恶意的 SQL 语句拼接至数据库查询中。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该参数执行任意 SQL 命令，进而读取、篡改或删除数据库中的敏感数据，甚至在特定配置下进一步获取系统权限。该漏洞影响所有安装了 Canteen 1.0 组件的 Joomla! 站点，攻击条件仅需目标站点对外开放 Web 服务且存在该缺陷组件，利用方式简单，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4977"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-11-01T22:55:04.023","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:54.267","remediation":"由于 Joomla! Canteen (com_canteen) 组件 1.0 存在 SQL 注入漏洞且厂商已停止维护，建议立即从 Joomla! 后台卸载并彻底删除该扩展。若业务必须使用，应在代码中对 index.php 传入的 mealid 参数强制类型转换为整型（intval）并使用参数化查询/预处理语句，同时部署 WAF 拦截含 SQL 关键字的恶意请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/66031","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1007-exploits/joomlacanteen-lfisql.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/40503","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8495","http://www.salvatorefresta.net/files/adv/Canteen%20Joomla%20Component%201.0%20Multiple%20Remote%20Vulnerabilities-04072010.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/512170/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41358","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/60103","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34250","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4977.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4977.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4977-2019.yaml","https://github.com/w4n95/vuls-data-raw-exploit-inthewild/blob/2c8c2568a21a9cc77244882f65c37bca47d71613/2010/CVE-2010-4977.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4977_40.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/27/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-4977-2018.yaml","https://github.com/chessredoffsec/nuclei-templates/blob/bf798045b1c57839b4998bf6e08c74fbfd076879/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml","https://github.com/wpsec/ARL-Source-Install/blob/aecf83f1f55a6f1a1a67dbe25e22ea0eb5a44bf2/tools/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4977.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0113.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0112","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4769","title":"Janguo Jimtawl 组件 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Jimtawl（com_jimtawl）组件 1.0.2 存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞，根源在于其对用户传入的 `task` 参数未做充分的路径安全校验，未过滤 `../`（点点）序列。远程攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，可向 `index.php` 的 `task` 参数注入包含 `../` 的恶意路径，从而跨越 Web 根目录读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息），并可能借此造成其他未明确说明的安全影响。该漏洞影响运行 Joomla! 并安装了 Jimtawl 1.0.2 组件的网站，攻击条件仅为目标站点存在该脆弱组件且可直接访问前端入口，利用方式简单，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4769"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-03-23T22:00:01.683","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:30.723","remediation":"立即升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Janguo Jimtawl (com_jimtawl) 1.0.2 组件，改用官方已修复的版本；若暂无法升级，请登录 Joomla! 后台在「扩展管理」中禁用或移除该组件，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中拒绝 index.php 中 task 参数包含 `../` 序列的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/42324","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15585","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/44992","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15585","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4769.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4769.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4769.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fcc97d3f09074a6534df65087e2097c6145b988b/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4769.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-4769-2013.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2010/CVE-2010-4769.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-4769_1.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4769-2013.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-4769-2012.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-4769-2014.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0112.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0111","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4719","title":"Fxwebdesign Com Jradio 路径遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 平台的 Fxwebdesign JRadio（com_jradio）组件在 1.5.1 之前版本中存在目录遍历漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，导致远程攻击者可在 controller 参数中插入\"../\"等目录遍历序列，从而突破 Web 根目录限制，读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码等）。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，影响所有运行受影响版本 JRadio 组件的 Joomla! 站点，可能导致敏感信息泄露，进而为进一步的入侵提供条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4719"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-02-01T23:00:03.437","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:24.880","remediation":"建议将 Joomla! 的 JRadio (com_jradio) 组件升级至 1.5.1 或更高版本，可从官方扩展目录重新下载安装以覆盖存在漏洞的旧版。若无法立即升级，可在 Joomla! 后台禁用或卸载 com_jradio 组件，并通过 Web 服务器规则（如 Apache 的 .htaccess）拒绝对外界暴露 index.php 中 controller 参数的非预期目录遍历字符（../ 等），作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/files/view/96751/joomlajradio-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/42600","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15749","http://www.fxwebdesign.nl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=20&Itemid=56","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/45440","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/64143","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15749","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4719.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4719.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4719-2009.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-4719-2007.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4719_23.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-4719_3.yaml","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4719.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4719_21.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0110","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4617","title":"Joomla! JotLoader 组件 目录遍历本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JotLoader（com_jotloader）组件 2.2.1 版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 section 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，远程攻击者可在该参数中插入 \"../\" 等目录遍历序列，从而读取目标服务器上任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码等）。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向受影响站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，影响所有运行 JotLoader 2.2.1 的 Joomla! 站点，可能导致敏感信息泄露与进一步入侵。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4617"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-29T22:33:32.633","updated":"2026-06-16T23:25:11.130","remediation":"建议立即将 JotLoader 组件升级至官方发布的 2.2.2 或更高版本（修复了 section 参数的目录遍历过滤）。若暂无法升级，可在 Joomla 后台禁用或卸载 com_jotloader 组件，并在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中通过 mod_security 规则拦截包含 ../ 及 null 字节的 section 参数请求，同时在 php.ini 中设置 open_basedir 限制文件访问范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/files/view/96812/joomlajotloader-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15791","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/64223","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15791","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4617.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4617.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4617.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fcc97d3f09074a6534df65087e2097c6145b988b/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4617.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-4617-2006.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4617.js","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4617_17.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-4617-2004.yaml","https://github.com/rjp2525/cve-data/blob/2f3ce5ef3a11f37d0a2e7d88f12b74499612a438/2010/CVE-2010-4617.json","https://github.com/ByteLobo/joomla/blob/32cae09fae17c01b9f6627cf8f2fb46045643162/templatesfuncional/CVE-2010-4617.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/z-11753.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0109","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4282","title":"Pandora FMS 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Pandora FMS 在 3.1.1 版本之前存在多个目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 ajax.php 的 page 参数、general/pandora_help.php 的 id 参数，或 operation/agentes/networkmap.php 的 layout 参数传入包含 \"../\" 等路径遍历序列的特制请求，利用 PHP 本地文件包含机制读取、包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。其中 networkmap.php 的 layout 参数更可被滥用来创建、修改或删除任意本地文件。该漏洞影响所有 3.1.1 之前的 Pandora FMS 版本，攻击仅需网络访问 Web 接口即可发起，无需登录凭证，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4282"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-12-02T17:15:00.597","updated":"2026-06-16T23:24:30.327","remediation":"建议立即升级 Pandora FMS 至 3.1.1 或更高版本。若暂时无法升级，可在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截包含目录遍历序列（如 ../）的 page、id、layout 参数请求，并限制 ajax.php、pandora_help.php、networkmap.php 的访问权限为仅可信 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/69543","http://osvdb.org/69544","http://osvdb.org/69545","http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2010/Nov/326","http://secunia.com/advisories/42347","http://sourceforge.net/projects/pandora/files/Pandora%20FMS%203.1/Final%20version%20%28Stable%29/pandorafms_console-3.1_security_patch_13Oct2010.tar.gz/download","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15643","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/514939/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/45112","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4282.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4282.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4282.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-4282.js","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-4282-2001_1.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-4282-1999.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder5/cve-2010-4282-2002.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-4282_4.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/35fe940be4a8cc841207d0ee607b7714e4ad436d/2010/CVE-2010-4282.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/20/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-4282_25.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0109.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0107","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0107.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-4231","title":"Camtron CMNC-200 IP 摄像机 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Camtron CMNC-200 全高清网络摄像机及 TecVoz CMNC-200 百万像素网络摄像机（固件版本 1.102A-008）的 Web 管理界面存在目录遍历漏洞。其 HTTP 服务在处理请求 URI 时未对 ../ 路径序列进行充分过滤与规范化校验，导致路径穿越防护失效。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向设备 80 端口发送包含 ../ 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，即可绕过目录限制读取设备文件系统上的任意文件，如配置文件、用户凭据等敏感信息。攻击仅需网络可达目标且无需登录凭证，影响上述固件版本的设备，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-4231"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-11-17","updated":"2026-07-15","remediation":"由于厂商未发布正式补丁，建议在网络边界通过 ACL 限制仅授权管理 IP 访问摄像头 Web 管理端口（80/443），并使用 VLAN 隔离防止横向访问；如必须暴露 Web 界面，请在反向代理上启用 WAF 规则拦截包含 ../ 等目录遍历载荷的请求，并定期审计设备配置文件访问日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15505","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/514753/100/0/threaded","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-4231.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-4231.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/2010/4xxx/CVE-2010-4231.json","https://github.com/K3ysTr0K3R/CVE-2010-4231-EXPLOIT"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0107.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0002","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0219","title":"Apache Axis2 默认管理员口令漏洞","description":"Apache Axis2 存在默认管理员口令漏洞，其 admin 账户默认密码为 axis2。攻击者可通过该默认凭证登录 Axis2 管理控制台，上传恶意打包的 Web 服务（.aar 文件）实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 SAP BusinessObjects Enterprise XI 3.2、CA ARCserve D2D r15 等集成 Axis2 的产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议修改默认口令或禁用管理控制台以进行修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0219"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-10-18T17:00:03.457","updated":"2026-06-16T23:15:44.017","remediation":"针对 Apache Axis2 默认口令漏洞，建议立即修改 Axis2 admin 账户默认密码（原为 axis2），在 axis2.xml 或配置界面中设置强密码；SAP BusinessObjects 用户需应用 SAP Security Note 1432881 更新 dswsbobje.war 组件；CA ARCserve D2D r15 用户应安装最新安全补丁；同时通过防火墙限制对 Axis2 服务端口（如 8080/8443）的访问，仅允许可信 IP 调用管理接口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://retrogod.altervista.org/9sg_ca_d2d.html","http://secunia.com/advisories/41799","http://secunia.com/advisories/42763","http://spl0it.org/files/talks/source_barcelona10/Hacking%20SAP%20BusinessObjects.pdf","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15869","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/989719","http://www.osvdb.org/70233","http://www.rapid7.com/security-center/advisories/R7-0037.jsp","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/514284/100/0/threaded","http://www.securitytracker.com/id?1024929","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/2673","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/62523","https://kb.juniper.net/KB27373","https://service.sap.com/sap/support/notes/1432881","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15869","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0219.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0219.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/5a90ffc0ef6ba2a3b04b8dd82941b2be8bb4cca7/2010/CVE-2010-0219.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0219.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0219-1490.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Axis2/CVE-2010-0219.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-0219_1.yaml","https://github.com/cqr-cryeye-forks/goby-pocs/blob/ffef890592ee0c35c94a148c9f7b96b8728036d4/Axis2-Default-Credentials-Remote-Code-Execution-(CVE-2010-0219).json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e61be9425da7cd98fab7bf6d914282e65c9f9042/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-0219.json","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-0219.js","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-0219_8.yaml","https://github.com/vvts-alpha/CVE-2010-0219"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0002.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2010/EXP-AVE-2010-0002.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0104","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-3426","title":"Joomla! Jphone 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! JPhone 组件 1.0 Alpha 3 版本的 jphone.php 文件存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入 ../ 目录遍历序列，包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 使用 JPhone 组件 1.0 Alpha 3 版本的站点，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类型。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意 controller 参数实现本地文件包含，进而可能导致敏感文件读取或代码执行。ExploitDB 已公开相关利用代码。Joomla! 官方已发布更新版本修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-3426"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-09-16T22:00:03.267","updated":"2026-06-16T23:22:44.687","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! 站点中已停更的 JPhone (com_jphone) 1.0 Alpha 3 组件（后台「扩展-管理」中卸载），并删除 /components/com_jphone 与 /modules 下相关文件。若必须保留，应升级到官方后续修复版本或在 jphone.php 中对 controller 参数使用 basename() 过滤并限制白名单，同时在 .htaccess 中拒绝含 \"..\" 的请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1009-exploits/joomlajphone-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14964","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/43147","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/61723","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14964","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3426.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-3426.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3426.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-3426.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-3426-1992.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-3426-1990.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-3426_12.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3426.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-3426-1992.yaml","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/2010/CVE-2010-3426.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/20/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0103","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-3203","title":"Joomla! PicSell 组件 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 PicSell（com_picsell）组件 1.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。该组件在处理 index.php 的 prevsell dwnfree 动作时，未对 dflink 参数进行充分的路径过滤与校验，攻击者可构造包含 \"../\"（点-点-斜杠）序列的恶意参数值，突破 Web 根目录限制，实现任意文件读取。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发该漏洞，从而读取服务器上的敏感文件（如配置文件、源码、口令文件等），可能导致信息泄露乃至进一步渗透。受影响范围为安装了 PicSell 1.0 组件且未打补丁的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-3203"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-09-03T18:00:02.577","updated":"2026-06-16T23:22:22.070","remediation":"建议立即升级 Joomla! 至 1.5.22 或更高版本，并卸载或禁用 PicSell (com_picsell) 1.0 组件；若无法升级，请在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截包含 ../ 的 dflink 参数请求，并限制 Web 服务器进程对敏感目录的读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/41187","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14845","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14845","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3203.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-3203.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3203.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bb86e46de27f177abd11211a1c508ec72b4b0dea/cves/2010/3xxx/CVE-2010-3203.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-3203-1988.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-3203-1986_3.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-3203_6.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/2010/3xxx/CVE-2010-3203.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2023/Jan/22/Reports/Report.csv","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-3203-1986.yaml","https://github.com/abh2technology/abh2-custom-templates-nucleiengine/blob/c7ba146f8016161974a9cf9f812ae7f225d23065/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-3203.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0069","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0069.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1870","title":"Apache Struts2 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Apache Struts2 2.0.0 至 2.1.8.1 版本中的 XWork 组件存在 OGNL 表达式求值漏洞（S2-005），由于 OGNL 广泛的表达式求值能力使用了宽松的白名单机制，远程未授权攻击者可通过构造恶意 OGNL 表达式，利用 #context、#_memberAccess、#root、#this、#_typeResolver、#_classResolver、#_traceEvaluations、#_lastEvaluation、#_keepLastEvaluation 等上下文变量绕过 ParameterInterceptors 中的 \"#\" 字符保护机制，修改服务端上下文对象并执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Apache Struts2 2.0.0～2.1.8.1 版本及基于此构建的 Atlassian Fisheye、Crucible 等产品，攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，可导致服务器完全被接管。该漏洞不同于 CVE-2008-6504，属于独立的 OGNL 表达式注入漏洞，CVSS 评分 5.0（中等严重度）。官方已在 Struts 2.2.0 版本中修复该漏洞，建议用户升级至 2.2.0 或更高版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1870"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-08-17T20:00:03.407","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:29.683","remediation":"升级到 Apache Struts 2.2.0 或更高版本，该版本默认收紧了 OGNL 表达式的白名单并修复 `#_memberAccess` 保护机制绕过问题。若无法立即升级，可在自定义 Action 中实现 `ParameterNameAware` 接口，在 `acceptableParameterName` 中拒绝包含 `#`、`(`、`)` 等字符的参数名以阻断 OGNL 上下文变量注入；同时在 Web 应用防火墙(WAF)规则中拦截含 `#context`、`#_memberAccess`、`#root` 等字符串的请求参数作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://blog.o0o.nu/2010/07/cve-2010-1870-struts2xwork-remote.html","http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/FISHEYE/FishEye+Security+Advisory+2010-06-16","http://packetstormsecurity.com/files/159643/LISTSERV-Maestro-9.0-8-Remote-Code-Execution.html","http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2010/Jul/183","http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2020/Oct/23","http://secunia.com/advisories/59110","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8345","http://struts.apache.org/2.2.1/docs/s2-005.html","http://tools.cisco.com/security/center/content/CiscoSecurityAdvisory/cisco-sa-20140709-struts2","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14360","http://www.osvdb.org/66280","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41592","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14360","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1870.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1870.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1870.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24b6c514a7b18b3a83429b0eaa19c9cb61a02fb8/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1870.json","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/info/cve-2010-1870-1817.yaml","https://github.com/govbk/WIKI-POC-EXP/blob/7d1194429dab9f9dd8139408e79b70ddb41a468f/%E9%9B%B6%E7%BB%84%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/160-Apache%20Struts/005-%EF%BC%88CVE-2010-1870%EF%BC%89s2-005.md","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder3/cve-2010-1870-1819.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/cve-2010-1870-2.yaml","https://github.com/zhzyker/vulmap/blob/3694afb7a3adec0b7f7c9027aab596e7b147c585/readme.md","https://github.com/SleepingBag945/dddd/blob/4c428a7c171275bfbb5fa72c2fb4bd7b48f4ff4a/common/config/pocs/CVE-2010-1870.yaml","https://github.com/KeepHowling/all_freaking_nuclei_templates/blob/b374318732b6922f72d327c57451a7d30973c0c6/CVE-2010-1870-2.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0069.toml"}]